HEADWORD: newsworthy
<hw>newsworthy</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Sufficiently interesting to be
reported in a newspaper; <as>as, a dog biting a man is not a
<ex>newsworthy</ex> item</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
